Alexis Arquette https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Alexis_Arquette 0 Alexis Arquette (July 28, 1969 – September 11, 2016) was an American actress, cabaret performer, underground cartoonist, and activist. She underwent gender transitioning in her late thirties, and supported other people making similar transitions.
